go-trafilatura — Apache-2.0
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Author:  markusmobius (Markus Mobius)
Source:  https://github.com/markusmobius/go-trafilatura

DERIVED FROM (attribution required). A faithful Go port of the Python original; the
core extraction algorithm is ported from it — the tag catalogs and attribute
whitelist (settings.go) are copied verbatim into src/core/constants.ts, and
docCleaning, the link-density heuristics, postCleaning, and the content-selector
rules are transcribed line-for-line (html-processing.go, internal/selector/content.go).

